{"about_the_game":"Man &amp; Dog is a hunting simulation game situated in Finland. Together with your companion dog, use real Nordic hunting methods to seek grouse bird hiding in the trees, or get into a thrilling chase with a fox or rabbit. Immerse yourself in authentic Finnish wilderness in autumm or winter. <br><br><br>Tree top bird hunting in winter or autumm<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/extras/sakoMetso.gif?t=1727605692\" /><br><br>The dog will try to point the correct tree where a bird is<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/extras/mantyMetso.gif?t=1727605692\" /><br><br>Keep an eye on the dog's path, and listen for barking<br>Dont get too excited, it could just be barking at a squirrell!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/extras/hakuLenkki.gif?t=1727605692\" /><br><br><br>Use foliage as cover and move carefully,  prey are elusive<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/extras/mantyMetso2.gif?t=1727605692\" /><br><br> Get a clear shot, branches might deflect bullets<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/extras/talviMetso.gif?t=1727605692\" /><br><br>Experience atmospheric black grouse swamp hunting <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/extras/teeriYlilento2.gif?t=1727605692\" /><br><br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> campaign and free play<br></li><li>use of proper hunting tactics is required to succeed<br></li><li>companion dog: works with the player, tries to find game from ground or trees<br></li><li>realistic ballistics and bullet physics simulation<br></li><li>realistic finnish terrain: spruce forests, swamps, pine forests, and mixed forests<br></li><li>dynamic weather and time of day<br></li><li>capercaillie, black Grouse, hazel Grouse, fox, rabbit<br></li><li>birds will perch in trees<br></li><li>seasons: autumn, winter</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727605692","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/page.bg.jpg?t=1727605692","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727605692","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727605692","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Man &amp; Dog is a hunting simulation game situated in Finland. Together with your companion dog, use real Nordic hunting methods to seek grouse bird hiding in the trees, or get into a thrilling chase with a fox or rabbit. Immerse yourself in authentic Finnish wilderness in autumm or winter. <br><br><br>Tree top bird hunting in winter or autumm<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/extras/sakoMetso.gif?t=1727605692\" /><br><br>The dog will try to point the correct tree where a bird is<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/extras/mantyMetso.gif?t=1727605692\" /><br><br>Keep an eye on the dog's path, and listen for barking<br>Dont get too excited, it could just be barking at a squirrell!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/extras/hakuLenkki.gif?t=1727605692\" /><br><br><br>Use foliage as cover and move carefully,  prey are elusive<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2794480/extras/mantyMetso2.